<a name="cor"></a>
<b>Correction</b><p>

  In a sidebar called "PBS's 'Democracy Project' : Is It Really The Democrat Project?" in 
our February, 1996 issue (vol.1, no.1),  Foundation Watch erred  in stating that Senator 
Jay Rockefeller represents Virginia. In fact, Rockefeller is the junior Senator from West 
Virginia.<p>
