<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000239-B033-351</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/cir/dr/dr964i.html 204.71.237.86 19970108035650 text/html 4551
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
